Dunes For Miles | Khongoryn Els, 🇲🇳 Mongolia
///replanted.migrated.viewer
The sand dunes at Khongoryn Els in the Gobi are quite spectacular and a definitely must-visit for any trip to Mongolia. The dune field is over 100km long and can have dunes up to 300 metres tall! This photo from above shows just how expansive they are!
